title: 10pcs Wearable Nail Soak Cap 4 Uv Acrylic Color Removal
description: For artificial nail removal. Trim excess nail. Carefully pour pure acetone to top of clear container (for easy access, use a plastic dropper). Carefully insert fingernail into liquid chamber by twisting. To release any pressure & avoid spillage during insertion, slightly squeeze to allow air to escape. Leave nail soaking 5 to 10 minutes to allow acetone to melt the artificial nail material.
